# Reporting view: spend and token usage grouped by provider, model, and day
Output tools/vhs/.render.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1500
Set Height 900
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type "sh tools/vhs/.demo/run.sh"
Enter
Sleep 9s
Type "4"
Sleep 1s
Show
Sleep 2s
Screenshot assets/reporting.png
Sleep 1s
